<section class="w-full bg-white py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-6">
    
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#003366] text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
      O que nossos alunos dizem
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
      
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between h-full transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300">
        <div>
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-6 text-yellow-400 fill-current">
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#003366] text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mb-8">
            "Nunca imaginei que conseguiria usar um computador. Com o leitor de tela e as aulas adaptadas, aprendi tudo e hoje trabalho em casa como digitadora."
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <%= image_tag "maria.jpg", alt: "Maria Aparecida", class: "w-12 h-12 md:w-14 md:h-14 rounded-full object-cover shadow-sm" %>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#003366] text-sm md:text-base">Maria Aparecida</h4>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500">Deficiência Visual</p>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-blue-500 mt-0.5">Informática Básica</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between h-full transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300">
        <div>
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-6 text-yellow-400 fill-current">
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#003366] text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mb-8">
            "As legendas e o intérprete de Libras fizeram toda a diferença. Hoje tenho meu próprio negócio de artesanato e emprego outras pessoas surdas."
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <%= image_tag "joao.jpg", alt: "João Carlos", class: "w-12 h-12 md:w-14 md:h-14 rounded-full object-cover shadow-sm" %>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#003366] text-sm md:text-base">João Carlos</h4>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#003366] text-sm md:text-base">João Carlos</h4>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500">Deficiência Auditiva</p>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-blue-500 mt-0.5">Empreendedorismo Social</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between h-full transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300">
        <div>
            <div class="flex gap-1 mb-6 text-yellow-400 fill-current">
                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            </div>
          <p class="text-[#003366] text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mb-8">
            "A plataforma funciona perfeitamente com meu software de controle por voz. Consegui aprender inglês e agora trabalho em atendimento ao cliente internacional."
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <%= image_tag "ana.jpg", alt: "Ana Paula", class: "w-12 h-12 md:w-14 md:h-14 rounded-full object-cover shadow-sm" %>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#003366] text-sm md:text-base">Ana Paula</h4>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500">Deficiência Física</p>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-blue-500 mt-0.5">Inglês Básico Acessível</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>